    <template>
      Sure, I can help you manage workplace stress. Here are some tips:
      1. Identify stressors and try to address them directly.
      2. Practice relaxation techniques like deep breathing or meditation.
      3. Set realistic goals and prioritize tasks.
      4. Take short breaks during the day to recharge.
      5. Maintain a healthy work-life balance.
      6. Reach out to a trusted colleague or supervisor for support.
      7. Consider talking to a professional if stress persists.
    </template>
