    <pattern>WORKPLACE CALMNESS</pattern>
    <template>
      To relax at work, you can try the following:
      1. Take short breaks to stretch and breathe deeply.
      2. Listen to soothing music with headphones.
      3. Practice mindfulness and stay in the present moment.
      4. Keep a stress ball or fidget toy at your desk.
      5. Consider a quick walk outside for fresh air and sunlight.
      6. Delegate tasks when possible to reduce workload.
      Remember, it's important to find what works best for you.
    </template>
  </category>

  <category>
    <pattern>MANAGING WORKLOAD</pattern>
